								{
									"id": "en_GB",
									"type": "STRING",
									"value": "Life gets busy and complicated. Some days you don't feel like you have the time, or the energy, for a run. Keep things simple with this adidas Own the Run t-shirt. It's soft, comfortable and quick-drying. Plus it's made with recycled materials, part of adidas' commitment to creating a more sustainable future. So you can feel good about the shirt on your back when you lay down those miles."
